{"tid":2356254,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方嚴厲譴責「香港自由之書」發表帖文抹黑警隊 唯恐天下不亂","createTime":"2021-01-06T16:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T05:54:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":480,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"0c517ec5bdae13df2db05770cfe8729f684dc63c","tid":2356254,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"香港自由之書FB: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5ibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=42e12c68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日(6日)下午，社交媒體專頁「香港自由之書」發表帖文，聲稱有人於前晚(5日)被警方拘捕，在拘留期間被吐口水、襲擊及不人道對待，更指控有警隊「國安人員」向被捕人表示，即使投訴亦沒有用。<br />\n<br />\n警方就此嚴正澄清，有關帖文內容毫無事實根據，該專頁在不提供案件詳情下對警隊作出性質嚴重的惡意指控。事實上，前晚國安處人員並無會見或拘捕任何人，而投訴警察課亦沒有接獲任何相關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n警方嚴厲譴責別有用心之徒唯恐天下不亂，捏造事實，意圖抹黑警隊，煽動仇恨，分化社會。倘若有人試圖以假消息蒙騙市民捐款，警方必定嚴肅跟進。"},{"pid":"6022c860ee1ef4a65ca7b765bc5605c62f83a6aa","tid":2356254,"uid":300006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"死黑警"},{"pid":"e04655592c4571ccce056ad2d36080f2bf1ed7f6","tid":2356254,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce36bca4ad770ce35393b4cecd567e3dffd29a7","tid":2356254,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm